msgstr "ວໍລຸມ RAID \"%s\" ທີ່ລະບຸດ້ວຍ --useexisting ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ຈິງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/custom/custom_partitioning.py:650
#, python-format
