msgstr "ກຸ່ມວໍລຸມ \"%s\" ທີ່ກຳນົດໃນຄຳສັ່ງ volgroup ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ຈິງ."

#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/custom/custom_partitioning.py:820
#, python-format
