#: pyanaconda/modules/storage/partitioning/custom/custom_partitioning.py:934
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No volume group exists with the name \"%s\".  Specify volume groups before "
"logical volumes."
msgstr "ບໍ່ມີກຸ່ມວໍລຸມຊື່ \"%s\". ໃຫ້ລະບຸກຸ່ມວໍລຸມກ່ອນວໍລຸມໂລຈິກ."

